Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了 對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:38.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.86,0:22:44.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.31,0:22:49.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.57,0:22:55.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇跡也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.92,0:23:08.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.80,0:23:19.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.56,0:23:27.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.94,0:23:32.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.36,0:23:43.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.29,0:00:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要說到秋天尋寶的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團要向暗號挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.02,0:01:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太陽的秘密(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.12,0:01:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要去的別墅真的藏有寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.68,0:01:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.14,0:01:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要用你們的智慧去找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我們少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的寶藏都會屬於我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.34,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.05,0:02:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是之前叫我買的那堆玩具吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪灰原那傢伙才不想跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你最近還很慷慨 這輛車也是新買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.75,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成博士你做了什麼東西來打劫銀行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經病 我怎麼可能會那麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.93,0:02:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的朋友的公司找我幫他們開發新玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了一大筆的合約金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.53,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人變聲器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士今天早上也送給我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個假面超人變聲器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人變聲器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以錄自己的聲音 然後轉變成其他的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是假面超人的新產品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和蝴蝶結變聲器一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.44,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 你一直看不起的我的發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要全國各地銷售了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的是博士叔父的別墅嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我叔父叫做阿笠栗介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這一帶有名的大富豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.46,0:03:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在50年前把一大筆財產藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次我想借助你們少年偵探團的智慧幫我找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:04:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不是博士事先來這裡將寶物藏起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士是不會騙我們小孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不笨嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從這間房間開始找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.42,0:04:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.09,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的叔父就是畫中那個男人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.77,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.86,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來博士的叔父的確是個有錢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.56,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 畫中背後的暖爐和這裡的一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說特地請人來這裡畫肖像畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣做的 就是有錢人家的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.02,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這是叔父病逝一年前請一位年輕畫家畫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起的那位女性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是為了照顧叔父而搬來這裡一起住的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是叔父唯一信賴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在這附近的小學教書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父死後她也回娘家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的50年這裡都沒有人來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡東西還真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些書籍 餐具…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為叔父的遺囑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間別墅在我死後50年之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要改變任何東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然並沒有什麼財產留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也決定下個月要拆掉它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你想趁被拆之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這佈滿灰塵的別墅中和小鬼們玩尋寶遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.73,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂翻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.52,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心留意周圍 一定可以發現到什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.38,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 例如我的腳下刻的那些怪字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,モ ザ リ サ ワ ソ デ ル
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英文嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 一定是阿拉伯文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就算是新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.21,0:07:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這次連新一也被我的問題給難倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.74,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪 我用了三天三夜想出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.27,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果博士是說你藏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在對面寢室的床底下找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有打開來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用布蓋上然後推進去了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有勞你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.05,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我在想的是這個別墅的另外一個謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個謎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對這東西有何看法 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是一個普通的一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在床邊撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我掉的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.66,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面全是灰塵 而且附近沒有它滾過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這枚一元硬幣的首次發行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是40年前的1955年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它竟然在這別墅裡 還佈滿灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.02,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…這無人的別墅 有人擅自闖入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止進來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這裡住過一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是個手指非常靈活的老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住過…手指靈活…老人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然博士拿一枚一元硬幣出來和那個硬幣比較看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.47,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做比較… 哪裡不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.94,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比我的硬幣還薄 而且還小了一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從原來的硬幣削出來變成縮水的一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的手工非常厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個「國」字也變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道這是故意的還是失誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過會用以前的那個「國」字 都是上了年紀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.77,0:09:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你怎麼知道是住在這裡的人做出來的東西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 的確是在這裡做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一邊看書一邊做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書本裡面夾著製造硬幣的金屬片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些白頭髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒有人可以在短時間之內刻出這樣的一元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就證明這個人長時間住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可能是消磨時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還不能肯定是不是只有一個老人住在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有小朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子住過這裡的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這花瓶的底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.51,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小孩子亂畫的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西我也有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這燭臺的底下也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盤子的背面也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是個頑皮的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.35,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是快去解開地板的暗號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.33,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 叔父應該沒有小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道住在這裡的神秘老人是帶著孩子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「跳舞的人偶」嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞的人偶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指夏洛克•福爾摩斯小說裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些人偶排隊跳舞的奇妙圖案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.36,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那是畫成小孩子的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道這個也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶和燭臺和盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較裡面的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊三個完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這是個有規律的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.72,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你會讀那些暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人的謎 一元硬幣的謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是不明白越是興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心底壓抑不住的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說偵探的血在沸騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.17,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 我覺得這些圖形 好像在哪里見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？ 你在哪看過 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來想一想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上寫的那些暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要在那裡偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.11,0:12:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,モ ザ リ サ ワ ソ デ ル
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不明白是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過通常這類的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.69,0:12:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多用前一個或後一個文字寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們試著退後一個文字讀出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.50,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟…著…箭…頭…走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著箭頭走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們去找箭頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來這間房間的時候不是會先看到一個箭頭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那種東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看那個時鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時鐘怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得那6點半有點奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是壞掉停下來而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們仔細看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的時鐘如果是六點半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時針與分針應該是會分開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它們卻是重疊在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示有人故意移動過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是藏起寶藏的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那個時鐘的針就是第一個箭頭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來就是找那時鐘的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有一堆撲克牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到中間的黑桃A了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不知為何用圖釘固定起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 A就是箭頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洋棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 這棋子的排列方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排列方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.37,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看就是箭頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.92,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還黏上膠水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.82,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.78,0:14:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有箭頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是收藏寶物的人最傷腦筋的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.98,0:14:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看門對面的桌子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三個點沒有灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是證明上面原來放有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指這掉到地上的飛機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.05,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它照著痕跡放回桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.16,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機指向床耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想寶物就在這床裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床的下面好像有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定就是寶箱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確在桌子上放了架飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不記得有弄倒它啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點打開 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.18,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用刀子割成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是收藏寶物的人想嚇我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 博士是不會那樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說這些玩具是博士藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.29,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了和你們在這裡玩尋寶遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是博士在放好離開之後到我們來這裡這段期間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有人來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那傢伙大概看到博士留下的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到寢室的寶箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後看到裡面全是玩具後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惱羞成怒 用刀割爛它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士放在桌上的飛機會掉到地上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個時候弄掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人為什麼要來這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可能是偶然經過好奇之下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就是為了找什麼東西而來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許和那些圖案有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖案？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.64,0:16:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們發現的那些太陽 月亮 星星的詭異圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說那些是暗號？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.18,0:17:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這間別墅裡真的有寶藏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 警方怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說大概是惡劣的小偷幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.96,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天會來調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家最好什麼都不要碰 就這樣離開比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 雖然對那些暗號很好奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想再弄亂現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出更多的暗號 然後找出寶藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.65,0:17:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 犯人可能還在附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張撲克牌後面也有暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我和步美找一樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太和光彥去找二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太多疑了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又發現了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果後來又發現了7個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲克牌 法文字典 唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機 酒杯 肖像畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.74,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來我聽阿姨說過 叔父生前很喜歡這種娃娃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有最先找到的3個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.27,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子 燭臺 花瓶  一共10個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些東西放在這裡也不知道是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有再長些一點的 像是文章之類的就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如日記或者信這類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.58,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信 就是信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嘛 那個圖形在哪裡見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前阿姨曾給我看過 我完全忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的阿姨就是這畫中的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說她以前當過小學老師的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.81,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那是五六年前的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說從10年前開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都有封沒寄信人地址和名字的信寄給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很奇怪 所以阿姨拿給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得內容全部都是用平假名寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.99,0:20:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像「老師您好」「保重身體」之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是她的學生寄的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.52,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是 因為十年來一直都是用平假名寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這的確很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.15,0:20:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些信和暗號有什麼關係呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面全部都畫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.52,0:20:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那些平假名的信的四周 就像一些花紋一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那些信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為完全看不懂 所以去請教你爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.43,0:20:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 住在附近的一個推理小說家好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給爸爸看過了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.97,0:20:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小說家因為沒有靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初不太高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他看到那些信以後 突然興奮起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拿著那些信回到屋子裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒幾分鐘就出來了 然後這樣對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.06,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把這封信交給你阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.88,0:21:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就像太陽一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你 我灰暗的心情被一掃而光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信裡面寫些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是暗號的解讀表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.23,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那個小說家發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些暗號都是平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平假名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.00,0:21:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 信的內容全是用平假名寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是指要用平假名去讀四周的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.38,0:21:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來寫那些信和畫這裡的暗號應該是同一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.08,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人為什麼要寫那些暗號給我阿姨呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不想讓阿姨以外的人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.36,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如他正在被某人跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.99,0:22:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阿姨曾經說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.81,0:22:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個怪人經常偷她的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.73,0:22:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那傢伙就是弄壞玩具的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.32,0:22:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個別墅果然不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.44,0:23:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的有寶藏嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.01,0:23:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.17,0:23:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是暗號 刻在地板上的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.42,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果將它們依照順序串聯起來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.94,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷…骷髏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.93,0:24:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.87,0:24:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.48,0:24:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮、星星和太陽的秘密(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.88,0:24:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.29,0:24:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20元紙幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次終於要解開暗號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.61,0:24:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
